MAINTAINERS: Add the driver info of the NXP IMX8QXP

The NXP i.MX 8QuadXPlus SOC has a new ADC IP. After adding
the driver support for it, I add the driver info of the
NXP IMX8QXP ADC to MAINTAINERS file.

